== White background for data cells ==

Add <code>class=srn-white-background</code> to the top line of the table  wikitext. It can be used on tables with inline cell or row background colors. Neither are affected by this class. 

This class is unnecessary if you are using this:
*'''{{tl|Static row numbers table}}'''
The class is incorporated into that template. 

